2. ğŸ’¡ Exploring Standard Deviation â€“ Intuition First

ğŸ‘£ Step-by-Step Understanding:
	1.	Find the Mean
	2.	Measure Distance from Mean for each point
	3.	Square those distances
	4.	Average them (using n for population, nâˆ’1 for sample)
	5.	Take square root â†’ Thatâ€™s your standard deviation!

ğŸ“– Real Life Analogy:
